<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Technology Hub</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background-color: yellow;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: grey;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background-color: yellow;
            color: black;
        }
        .section {
            padding: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: grey;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>Technology Hub</header>
    <nav>
        <a href="#about">About Us</a>
        <a href="#statistics">Statistics</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    
    <div id="about" class="section" style="background-color: white;">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Technology Hub, your go-to source for the latest tech news and insights.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div id="statistics" class="section" style="background-color: yellow;">
        <h2>Statistics</h2>
        <p>We provide up-to-date statistics on the latest technology trends and market movements.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div id="faq" class="section" style="background-color: white;">
        <h2>FAQ</h2>
        <p>Find answers to the most frequently asked questions about the tech world.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div id="contact" class="section" style="background-color: yellow;">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Reach out to us via email at contact@techhub.com</p>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        &copy; 2025 Technology Hub. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
